{
  "stem": "15943.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A very low pool of water with-- was disinfectant, that we-- we're supposed to be sterilized after they shaved the hair.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We went into showers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was water-- quick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But there-- but there was water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's when we find out from the people that were there, because we came into Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And Birkenau is the part of Auschwitz where either you went to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Or if you're lucky, you were sold eventually to slavery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the people over there were telling us who that person was that is there because people were there longer than you, and all those things.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I argued with a woman at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She was telling me-- [SIGHS] I smelled the stench, and I saw the smoke.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And she was telling me, they're burning your families here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I said, she's a liar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was with Karola and with Rifkele.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the one we went together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when we were put in-- in a barrack which had hundreds of people, and there were five people to a wooden plank.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One girl started screaming, she knew Rifkele.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And her name is Tola.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we stayed together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We managed to stay together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "From Auschwitz we were transported together, and we stayed till liberation together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Tola and Karola and I still stayed together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Rifkele's in Israel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were marched naked [SIGHS] after the hair was shaved.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we came in after the shower, a quick shower, and we were naked.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave whatever-- there was a pile of clothing, and they gave whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they gave me a long petticoat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was my clothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rifkele was tall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was short.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave Rifkele like a baby-doll dress.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and-- and she was embarrassed, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
